==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Illusionist
<hw>Il*lu"sion*ist</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One given to
illusion; a visionary dreamer.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A magician or conjurer who produces illusions by
sleight of hand; a prestidigitator.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Illusive</ent>⟦br⟧
